{
  "stem": "1511.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a lot of work involved.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am Sara Hertzberg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was born in Poland, in 1925, in a city of Wegrow, a province of Lublin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my family-- oh, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father's name was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] no, Yosef Szejnberg, and my mother's name was Shifra Szejnberg.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had three-- two sisters except me, and three brothers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the oldest one Velvel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The second one was Freidke.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The third one was Chavche.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then was Usher, Feivel, Chiel, and me, Sara.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was the youngest, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we come from-- he was from [NON-ENGLISH] rabbi's [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in our house was a shtiebel that we had a minyan or more people, just people, I suppose they were from the [NON-ENGLISH] rabbi's crowd.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every Saturday there was a special davenen in our house, was a davenen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when it comes Yom Tov, also they all gathered in our kitchen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That house was about five rooms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the first one was a kitchen and then it was beside-- was a room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the bedroom was divided.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in that first room where the kitchen was-- it was like a living room to us, maybe the dining room-- there was [NON-ENGLISH] and a [NON-ENGLISH] And there was the men were davening.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there was a little partition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the side where the bedroom was, the woman used to come to daven.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they mainly come when it was high holidays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that was going on for quite a few years, generation by generation, when I wasn't born yet.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I even remember my grandmother was living not far in a little city, not far from us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but the choir was my brothers.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
